longBusinessSummary: Emerald Health Therapeutics, Inc., together with its subsidiaries, engages in the production and sale of medical cannabis for medical purpose in Canada. It offers dried cannabis strains, pre-rolls, ingestible extracts, and cannabis oil products to its medical patients. The company distributes its medical products through licensed wholesale pharmacies and to licensed wholesale clients. It also exports medical cannabis products to licensed wholesale purchasers in Europe. The company was formerly known as T-Bird Pharma Inc. and changed its name to Emerald Health Therapeutics, Inc. in June 2015. Emerald Health Therapeutics, Inc. is headquartered in Vancouver, Canada.
